  <acronym>Co-HLM</acronym>
  <official_title>Cerebral Oxymetry at Elective Coronary and Valve Surgery: An Observational Study Using Norepinephrine to Maintain Arterial Blood Pressure on Cardio Pulmonary Bypass.</official_title>
